<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">19倍速算法，19与某数相乘时，可先将某数扩大20倍后，再减去上某数，即为其积。其口诀是：19先作20算，然后再将某数减。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×19=a×20-a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">36×19=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 36×19</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=36×20-36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=720-36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=684</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>